lead_paragraph: The Swiss Federal Court has cleared the way for former Nicaraguan soccer official Julio Rocha to be extradited to the United States after rejecting his appeal to be sent to his home country, the court said in a statement on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Swiss Court Clears Extradition of Ex-Nicaragua Soccer Boss Rocha to U.S.
headline.main: Swiss Court Clears Extradition of Ex-Nicaragua Soccer Boss Rocha to U.S.
